The Cut Django App: Contacts

===============
thecut.contacts
===============

This application requires ``thecut.authorship``.


To install this application (whilst in the project's activated virtualenv)::
    pip install git+ssh://git@git.thecut.net.au/thecut-contacts


Add the ``thecut.contacts`` to the project's ``INSTALLED_APPS`` setting::

    INSTALLED_APPS = (
        ...
        'thecut.contacts',
    )


If you would like to run the tests, install the requirements::
    pip install -r lib/python2.7/site-packages/thecut/contacts/tests/requirements.txt

Then run the tests for the application with::
    python manage.py test contacts
